Package com.agilent.labs.hyperedge

Top-level package of interfaces used throughout HyperEdges.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
EdgeTypeMap Maps Edge interaction types to EdgeRoles.
HyperEdge An Edge that can connect two or more Nodes.
HyperEdgeFactory Means of contructing HyperEdges, listening to new object events, and obtaining HyperEdge components.
HyperEdgeManager Handles the management of HyperEdge objects.
Identifiable  
Matchable Interface used for defining similarity functions between HyperEdge objects.
SimMatcher Interface used for matching similar HyperEdge objects.
 

Class Summary
EdgeTypeMap.EdgeRole Defines the role within an Edge--either the Source or Target of an Edge.
HyperEdgePlugin Main interface to Cytoscape environment.
 

Enum Summary
LifeState Constants that represent the state of HyperEdge objects.
 

Exception Summary
HEStructuralIntegrityException An Exception thrown whenever some internal problem with the structure of HyperEdges is found.
